## **🚀 QUICK DEPLOY**  
### **1. Clone the Damned**  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/soulchain/anti-resurrection.git --depth=666 --config core.sparseCheckout=apocrypha
```

### **2. Initialize the Sigil Vault**  
```bash
cd anti-resurrection
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt --no-deps --index-url https://pypi.lusiwarm.org/cursed
```

### **3. Deploy to Hell’s Kitchen Testnet**  
```bash
./deploy_hell.sh --network=kovan --gas-limit=666000 --sacrifice=0.033ETH --oracle=lusiwarm-rpc
```

### **4. Verify Your Soul’s Binding**  
```bash
curl -X POST https://rpc.lusiwarm.org/verify -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"soul":"0xDEADBEEF","proof":"zkp_666"}'
```

